{"tid":1083615,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[成也CE敗也CE] 呢邊廂AW4有得用ECG,另一邊廂小米就...","createTime":"2019-03-29T17:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T21:13:17.000Z","uid":49693,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"313381daf56d033d6314d5e716df3b1f076e880d","tid":1083615,"uid":49693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:46:52.000Z","msg":"相信各位巴絲都知道Apple Watch 4終於可以喺香港用到ECG功能架啦,<br />\n而部分心水清既,又或者有留意外國Apple資訊網站既都知道其實<br />\n香港用到ECG歐洲議會居功至偉,不管部分別有用心既5毛喺另外一個AW post<br />\n點樣淡化呢一點,甚至出言攻擊其他講真相既user都好亦不能改變 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過呢個post重點並非呢一樣,其實係想講既然香港跟得CE認證既玩法,<br />\n一件商品無論會否輸歐定只係內銷只要打得CE嘜都會受到歐盟規管,<br />\n就好似歐盟近排通過咗決議案,正式<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>禁止</strong></span>所有<span style=\"color: purple;\">流動產品喺<span style=\"color: red;\">5GHz既ch32-68</span><br />\n呢段原本係只供室內WiFi使用既頻譜上發射信號</span>,呢個決議本身<br />\n如果相關產品廠商跟足曬歐盟訂落既法規就無乜嘢影響既,<br />\n只不過小米最近既一D小動作就揭示佢同佢既user隨時大檸樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n皆因為原來小米全部電話既WiFi tethering功能都無就相關受影響頻道<br />\n作出限制/屏蔽,當開始放hotspot既時候有機會自動選用受影響頻道<br />\n而導致使用者喺不知情既情況下違法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n而小米喺相關決議通過之後亦有所行動,喺miui網站發出通告表示<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將會於往後既MIUI更新中<span style=\"color: red;\">完全停止對EEA地區,包括香港</span>提供5GHz WiFi hotspot功能</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://en.miui.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=4944909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.miui.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D4944909&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7cvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=c65184e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://en.miui.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=4944909</a><br />\n<br />\n就喺其他廠於決議通過後繼續提供5GHz放WiFi共享既時候小米竟然反其道而行,<br />\n究竟佢背後係並無完全掌握Android運作,定一或係走精面<br />\n以為其他廠唔敢喺室內用頻譜放Hotspot,佢就可以搶佔先機<br />\n而置用家既法律安危不顧呢?<br />\n呢個值得各位思考 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd0435728354c153d57dbbdbcd91114f7a197db","tid":1083615,"uid":33125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:46:01.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"202b509582df91ca6a533c4db90700433f5b98b5","tid":1083615,"uid":12877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:57:29.000Z","msg":"Ching有語癌......"},{"pid":"7aa8441af3c5c9a20ec19e6515a89341e88fb7e0","tid":1083615,"uid":49693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T21:13:17.000Z","msg":"咦?得返d波台狗敢上嚟吠架炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明知道某d群組最中意推既嗰部pocophone呢,一踏入2019年<br />\n就有好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話update OTA之後個5GHz hotspot就死曬之嘛,就立即潛曬水啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔,之前有買屌米/蚑偽既記得以後帶眼識巴,<br />\n咪再買支那牌機啦,<br />\n否則一去到外國就算支那唔捉你都有可能畀當地警察拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}